        <label>stick grenade belt</label>
        <description>Old-school fragmentation grenades strapped to a belt. They can be thrown a short distance, where they'll explode, damaging anything and anyone nearby. Can be reloaded using type 67 stick grenades.</description>
        <techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>
